data.description: Fresh new Look!!  This amazing home sits on .7 acres in the Pine Harbor area of Pell City.  Get ready to fall in love when you walk up on the large wrapped around covered porch that overlooks the large open flat yard.  You will see yourself, friends and family making so many memories here.  This home offers a master bedroom and bath on the 1st level, open living room that features a beautiful fireplace perfect for those chilly afternoons.  The kitchens is open and includes brand new appliances.  Once you go upstairs in the home you will find 3 large bedrooms large enough for any furniture you could put in it.  This home sits right across from Lake Logan Martin in a very peaceful neighborhood in Pell City but still just minutes from shopping and all that Pell City has to offer.
